KeyMaster Pro — third-party asset attribution
=============================================

Course sampled piano (assets/piano/salamander-lite/)
-----------------------------------------------------
Piano samples adapted from Salamander Grand Piano by Alexander Holm, licensed under Creative Commons Attribution 3.0 Unported.
Licence: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/
Source:  Salamander Grand Piano V3 (Yamaha C5), via the Tone.js public
         audio repository mirror (https://tonejs.github.io/audio/salamander/).

Adaptations made for KeyMaster Pro: a curated subset of 18 notes (every minor
third, A1-C6) was MIRRORED from the Tone.js public Salamander V3 set, then
re-encoded to MP3 (192 kbps, lossy compression), trimmed to roughly a
6-second decay, and given a 200 ms fade-out. Original Salamander note
filenames were kept (files were NOT renamed). The samples were NOT
loudness-normalised and are NOT looped.
